# Google OAuth — required for "Push to Google Sheets" in the Reports module.
# Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (type: Web application) in Google Cloud Console,
# enable the Google Sheets API, and add your app origin (e.g. the value of
# VITE_APP_URL and http://localhost:5173 for dev) to the "Authorized JavaScript
# origins" and "Authorized redirect URIs". Required scopes are requested at
# runtime: spreadsheets + drive.file. Leave blank to disable Sheets push (the
# Reports "Sheets" button then falls back to a CSV download).
VITE_GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=""
